name: ComparatorChain_compareTest
description: Unit tests for the ComparatorChain class, focusing on the compare method with various configurations of comparators.

test_cases.name: testCompare_SingleComparator_ForwardOrder
test_cases.description: Tests the compare method with a single comparator in forward order.

test_cases.name: testCompare_SingleComparator_ReverseOrder
test_cases.description: Tests the compare method with a single comparator in reverse order.

test_cases.name: testCompare_MultipleComparators_MixedOrder
test_cases.description: Tests the compare method with multiple comparators in mixed order.

test_cases.name: testCompare_NoComparators_ThrowsException
test_cases.description: Tests that the compare method throws an exception when no comparators are added.
